1. copy latest RNC to a new version (increase number in filename)
2. edit & save
3. convert to RNG
4. validate the XMLs

language description - http://relaxng.org/

convert rnc to rng - trang (standard repositories)
  trang job-<nn>.rnc job-<nn>.rng

validate - xmllint from libxml2-tools (standard repositories)
  xmllint --noout --relaxng job-<nn>.rng xmlfile.xml

Docs in old wiki: https://wiki.innerweb.novell.com/index.php/RD-OPS_QA/Automation/Technical/JobsXML

